    <note>Zhao(1) Shipeng [389] Qin(1) Gui's [8008] son-in-law. His son-in-law, Hong(1) Shouqing [3424] (q.v.), was Hong(1) Kuo's [870] cousin. Factional information. XNYL, 154.14a. See SS, 227.50a (PRC ed., 227.7001). for position in imperial genealogy. His S. Song address is not clear. His daughter married to a Raozhou, Poyang resident, but his nephew was the son-in-law of Gao(1) Shijian [3449], whose son, Gongxuan [912], was a Jizhou, Jian resident. For the time being, I am segmenting the lineage with Shipeng's father, Zhongtan [10942], and leaving them at their ancestral address, Kaifeng.</note>
